---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "@/components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "@/components/Footer.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Background - David Russell"
  description="David Russell - a decade in marketing, built his own startups, grew a Wix site into a marketplace doing over $400,000 a year. Now building best-in-class websites and marketing funnels."
>
  <Header />
  <main>
    <section class="essay">
      <a href="/" class="back">Back to home</a>
      <h1>Background.</h1>
      <p class="lede">
        I grew what started as a Wix site into a marketplace doing over $400,000 a year in sales. A decade of marketing experience behind it &mdash; building my own startups and consulting across dozens of industries. Now I'm building best-in-class websites and marketing funnels.
      </p>
      <div class="post-body">
        <p>
          The work has been the same shape for a long time: figure out what's actually useful, ship it cleanly, then keep tightening the loop between offer, audience, and the thing they buy. Some of it was mine end-to-end; a lot of it was alongside operators who needed a marketing brain that could also build the site, write the copy, and run the funnel.
        </p>
        <p>
          That experience &mdash; my own startups plus consulting across dozens of industries &mdash; now goes into best-in-class websites and marketing funnels for people who care about both ends: the craft of the site and the math of the funnel underneath it.
        </p>
        <p>
          If that's the kind of work you're looking for, the contact form on the home page is the fastest way in.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
